  "title": "Marketing & Sales Promotions Associate",
  "description": "<p><strong>Tired of hearing \"Do you have experience” or \"Minimum degree cert\"?</strong></p><p>We say — Your attitude matters more than your experience💪</p><p>Join our Sales & Marketing team, where you’ll learn how to run campaigns, meet people, and represent brands in exciting places — events, pop-ups, and roadshows across Singapore.</p><p>Every day is different. Every person you meet teaches you something new.<br /></p><p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><ul><li>Participate in face-to-face marketing campaigns for events and roadshows</li><li>Build relationships and create engaging experiences for potential customers</li><li>Coordinate with teammates to ensure smooth campaign execution</li><li>Provide timely feedback and updates on campaign progress</li></ul><p><strong>Here’s what you’ll get:</strong></p><p>🔥 1-on-1 mentorship and full training</p><p>🎉 A team that feels like friends</p><p>💰 Incentives and Bonuses</p><p>🚀 Career advancement (Team Leader and beyond)<br /></p><p>No experience? No worries, training is provided here.</p><p>We’re looking for individuals who are ready to move fast, think bigger, and learn everything on the go. Apply here to find out more!</p>",
